  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a romantic fantasy where past meets present! Experience a unique interactive game featuring Korea's stunning photoshoot models in this cinematic adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌙 <strong>ABOUT THIS GAME</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of Ha Dong-hun, Korea's most renowned photographer. Despite his successful career, he holds a secret that's about to unravel when a mysterious package arrives at his doorstep. In an extraordinary twist of fate, three royal concubines from the ancient Baran Kingdom suddenly appear in his modern-day life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the reincarnation of King Hadou, you'll navigate modern Seoul with three enchanting concubines, each portrayed by professional Korean photoshoot models. Will you unlock the mysteries of your past life while finding true love in the present?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/0b2d6da1e7a6d380c4d388d9b0c35607.poster.avif?t=1748233823\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/0b2d6da1e7a6d380c4d388d9b0c35607.webm?t=1748233823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/0b2d6da1e7a6d380c4d388d9b0c35607.mp4?t=1748233823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌙 <strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shape Your Story</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Create your own narrative through meaningful choices</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Experience different romantic routes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Discover multiple endings based on your decisions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/100207ca9eea6ecaeacbd6461a383548.poster.avif?t=1748233823\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/100207ca9eea6ecaeacbd6461a383548.webm?t=1748233823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/100207ca9eea6ecaeacbd6461a383548.mp4?t=1748233823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Meet Captivating Characters</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Suk-won: A quick-witted beauty adapting to modern life</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/4dfcabfd4de86446d7eee430e8e5e4b2.poster.avif?t=1748233823\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/4dfcabfd4de86446d7eee430e8e5e4b2.webm?t=1748233823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/4dfcabfd4de86446d7eee430e8e5e4b2.mp4?t=1748233823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Hae-in: The mysterious concubine with hidden depths</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/76ae2d25adf2ec8594d648aada6b3eb7.poster.avif?t=1748233823\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/76ae2d25adf2ec8594d648aada6b3eb7.webm?t=1748233823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/76ae2d25adf2ec8594d648aada6b3eb7.mp4?t=1748233823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Seung-a: The elegant noble concubine with timeless grace</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/2f509cc172a2a2f3fc1bc6fdbfafe396.poster.avif?t=1748233823\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/2f509cc172a2a2f3fc1bc6fdbfafe396.webm?t=1748233823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/2f509cc172a2a2f3fc1bc6fdbfafe396.mp4?t=1748233823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Premium Production Value</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- High-quality cinematics featuring professional photoshoot models</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Stunning visuals and dynamic scenes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Immersive storytelling</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/8231630f5bdd86a35570e10bfe196ecd.poster.avif?t=1748233823\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/8231630f5bdd86a35570e10bfe196ecd.webm?t=1748233823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3478200/extras/8231630f5bdd86a35570e10bfe196ecd.mp4?t=1748233823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌙 <strong>BONUS CONTENT</strong></h2><p class=